{"id": "fe5c837bc1312943444e33b94d85912089afbdb83a44af0d9da05c80be4ae58d", "item_id": "32c0138673:0", "text": "PxrAOVLight"}
{"id": "d5e2fe0d419a1be9f6209bda57e2f92cd0d464af6fb44b81fec508f347b58c26", "item_id": "32c0138673:1", "text": "is a handy utility light that allows a lighting artist to output a shot-specific AOV mask without needing to request one from the shading artists or generate a"}
{"id": "b12871e840d4a83e72dc900e2c9783c395dea63fb44d2cff035d63615baacf2e", "item_id": "32c0138673:2", "text": "/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19662011"}
{"id": "c484a5260c394ffe1e33e8d2a0115f7fd109d5eea4a2f49d5031f946e09c9f81", "item_id": "32c0138673:3", "text": "(LPE)."}
{"id": "4b39749d5c6b18a5ebfab096745f5bee204597857e7761c926966e0797c181db", "item_id": "32c0138673:4", "text": "Light Linking with PxrAovLight"}
{"id": "8560c07a7f710bdc51678b8be40daafb9d6f96e1ace9168ba04e7e98a531c635", "item_id": "32c0138673:6", "text": "Light Linking"}
{"id": "86e5b701b13ac8ebfe4c5f3e2e66d6d48e4aef4860516119ad3426a9584b0a4e", "item_id": "32c0138673:7", "text": "to include/exclude pieces of geometry in the AOV. In this example, the PxrAovLight is \"off\" globally and \"on\" the tree in the scene.  This linking set up creates creates a mask of the tree."}
{"id": "c9acbfbb3b4bb76d0f8e855ea3401a31d77f38242f44b950e5654a05a5796af9", "item_id": "32c0138673:8", "text": "Light Filters and PxrAovLight"}
{"id": "c499b8913cb39887e8774da8db8e23784d25dfdb26b4d6e930b888958b7a4202", "item_id": "32c0138673:9", "text": "Because PxrAovLight is a \"light\", we can add a light filters to modify the output AOV.  In this example, the"}
{"id": "69520493bbe1cafac9be955f3e2af6c5d9f04c4ea151c105aec2bf78a6f5456b", "item_id": "32c0138673:10", "text": "PxrIntMultLightFilter"}
{"id": "4e46ea9da0368b53f3ef018fd965307e5e2ea3f11b43f35c610f4a38a60e492e", "item_id": "32c0138673:11", "text": "is attached to PxrAovLight.  The Light Filter is only linked to the tree trunk, resulting in a gray value for the tree trunk mask."}
